title.rendered: JOVADI Presentation during Paris Haute Couture Week

content.rendered:
JOVADI Presents Carousel of Dreams High Jewelry Collection

Embark on a captivating journey with JOVADIs Carousel of Dreams collection, a symphony of design and inspiration that embodies the essence of our brands evolution.

This remarkable collection tells a compelling narrative, starting from the inception of our vision in 2018, weaving through the challenge of the times brought by the global pandemic, and culminating in the realization of our dream the opening of our flagship store in the city of Paris.

Our Carousel of Dreams collection invites you to embrace lifes magical moments. Each meticulously crafted piece represents a chapter in our extraordinary story.

This collection is a tribute to the essence of JOVADI  the dreams that inspired us, the challenges that fortified us, and the passion that has always driven us. It is a testament to the power of dreams and the relentless spirit of creativity, proving that even on lifes carousel, if you hold on, dreams do come true.

About JOVADI

JOVADI is a distinguished fine jewelry brand known for its dazzling handcrafted jewels designed for sophisticated women worldwide. Founded by Ella Peters, a trailblazing entrepreneur, JOVADI aims to make fine jewelry accessible to a diverse demographic often overlooked by top brands. As the first woman of color to establish a fine jewelry brand in Paris, Ella passionately expresses her creativity and love for jewelry design.

Established in 2018, JOVADI has a rich history rooted in family heritage and a passion for craftsmanship. The brand's name is derived from the founder's children and reflects the creative legacy spanning generations, originating from Africa and flourishing in Paris, the global capital of fine jewelry. JOVADI has achieved significant recognition, having partnered with Rolls Royce, featured in Vogue & Tater Magazine, and adorned celebrities like Nicky Hilton, Sabine Getty, and Priyanka Chopra.

Photo: Press JOVADI 

More on: @jovadijewellery


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
